{"tid":2510901,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"被HR暗寸「無料到」 求職者勁不滿︰你出萬五請個文員咋！","createTime":"2021-04-30T13:07:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T14:11:48.000Z","uid":19552,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6123d274ed42f3e304d1a49e166381ca0c4ac8b9","tid":2510901,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:07:14.000Z","msg":"不少打工仔都認為HR能夠反映一所企業的文化，而面試經歷也求職者了解公司文化的其中一環。如果見工經歷不愉快，即使公司最後提出Offer，求職者也不一定會接受。<br />\n<br />\n最近有求職者投稿，大呻見工時被HR暗寸，讓她內心非常不舒服，當下已有離開的念頭，並直言對方只是以一萬五千元聘請文員，不明白為何態度要如此高高在上，「呢啲工就算請我，我都唔會做！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQTB9GDdrhKwFPLmvtUdzC5RpuXouxesQrR5CC2cdvYPB?filename=2o1eThX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2o1eThX.jpg&h=490d9646&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfBUoAzYeSdhFTrt1nMwLhpkYFP828D86cs1tHB4RcXNi?filename=xgNBnbf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxgNBnbf.jpg&h=034135b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNU3xxWtgkxC6Md8XinZtvEzMeuWASBMHukUAWigFEaZq?filename=XQ7NtRf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXQ7NtRf.jpg&h=c4fd87cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWiTC6a1UrcT1oLwockDkx8dEQ3zK2L3HtS64kBHQFGYU?filename=2SiMKpy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2SiMKpy.jpg&h=2687d836&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSKrZqLQ8on9M3m3wmP52fPbrxfVbU7f5oTdJKv6CJfJ6?filename=P5kfCKx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP5kfCKx.jpg&h=dfbd1e58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRcySggoCx3cJTrJM5dXkdQUT7rB2ZBtXf6urn2bYtZZ7?filename=z1EzThQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz1EzThQ.jpg&h=cd8cd5ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs